data.description: This newly remodeled home is absolutely gorgeous and features 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths located on a quiet cul-de-sac. A private, detached casita is sure to delight any guest. This very desirable open floor plan boasts high ceilings and a grand fireplace in the great room and plantation shutters thru-out. Gourmet kitchen offers a large quartz island with waterfall sides. Beautiful cabinets, built-in stainless appliances and pantry. Dining area is spacious. Luxury awaits in the large master en-suite which is private from the other bedrooms. It also features a fireplace and large walk-in closet, double vanities and an amazing tiled open shower. The outdoors is postcard perfect and is designed for maximum outdoor living and offers the best in entertainment. The expansive backyard includes a specially designed custom BBQ island, large fire-pit, an oversized pergola and spacious pool and spa. The large pie shaped lot is very private and an entertainers paradise. This meticulously cared for home is in a small gated community of 33 homes. You will love the oversized 3 car garage which has A/C and beautiful epoxy floors. Low HOA's and minutes away from Premium Golf Courses, restaurants, hiking, biking and Polo Grounds. This home is a rare find and won't last long - a must see!
